  <brief_title>Study of an Investigational Drug, BMS-986089, in Ambulatory Boys With DMD</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-site, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Double-blind, Multiple Ascending Subcutaneous Dose Study to Evaluate the Safety Tolerability and Pharmacokinetics of BMS-986089 in Ambulatory Boys With Duchenne Muscular Dystrophy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
